  "title": "chore(examples): add e-commerce theme [part 3]",
  "body": "_This is part 3 of the series \"e-commerce demo\"._\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nThis adds the widget styles for the e-commerce theme. It doesn't yet add the demo-specific widget styles.\r\n\r\n## Notes\r\n\r\n- The theme styles are overriding the CSS classes generated by InstantSearch to later be extracted as a theme\r\n- The styles are alphabetically ordered\r\n- The main SearchBox style is part of the demo style (next PR)\r\n- The Hits style is part of the demo style (next PR)\r\n- The outlines were removed for now, waiting for a specific design\r\n- The Panel for the RangeInput takes the RangeSlider into account in the demo styles (next PR)\r\n- The RangeInput \"Go\" button remains unstyled because the design is missing\r\n- The ToggleRefinement style is by default aligned on the left (the demo styles will reverse the order in the next PR)\r\n- RatingMenu selected style is temporary until we've got a designer's POV\r\n\r\n## Preview\r\n\r\n[See preview →](https://deploy-preview-3801--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/examples/e-commerce/)\r\n\r\n## Related\r\n\r\n- [E-commerce demo design](https://app.zeplin.io/project/5acc8becfc0c980068fc12cc/screen/5cd1a7992e4f02039b5a8336)",
